{"tid":1468483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學習藍絲盲橕精神","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:56:18.000Z","uid":102005,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"31a04687e0e49ed8064a73ed19573b1823e52366","tid":1468483,"uid":102005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:52:49.000Z","msg":"If we burn, you burn with us.<br />\n<br />\n【手動轉】<br />\n<br />\n問：阻塞機場搞死香港？<br />\n答：「做法不完美，但可接受，要改善。」<br />\n<br />\n問：點解阻止公安離開？<br />\n答：「佢唔喺現場出現就冇事，去得果度就可能有呢啲風險」。<br />\n<br />\n問：阻止救護帶佢離開？人命嚟㗎。<br />\n答：「而家眾說紛云，我認為事主可以去報警先，警方必定會跟進調查。」<br />\n<br />\n問：點解你地咁冇人性，濫用暴力，究竟想點？<br />\n答：「在場嘅市民只係用最低武力，當一切平靜後，真誠對話就會展開。」<br />\n<br />\n對唔住，7.21、8.11血仍未乾，有人爆頭，有人失明，有人俾黑警打到成地血都冇收手，之後我從來冇聽過，警方有道歉有撤查。<br />\n<br />\n以上，全部係黑警同林鄭嘅對白。<br />\n<br />\n#不割 #不割 #不割 #核爆也不割 #保持隊型"},{"pid":"81f832050f85917e1dfbc09dc923c7bc810432f6","tid":1468483,"uid":285481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/241gDjd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F241gDjd.jpg&h=24184809&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L3FpNcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL3FpNcz.jpg&h=7d30142c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDEudSz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDEudSz.jpg&h=51c08fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RW360xA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRW360xA.jpg&h=82f5ceec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKyuYjf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKyuYjf.jpg&h=abda31c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SqmDREf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSqmDREf.jpg&h=86ba4115&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7jUudSB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna